title: TTU Baseball Recap: Tech outlasts Rice, 3-2 - KCBD
content: TTU Baseball Recap: Tech outlasts Rice, 3-2  KCBD
description: The No. 17 Texas Tech baseball team battled on a sun-splashed Saturday afternoon for a gritty 3-2 win against Rice at Reckling Park. The Owls tied the game, 2-2, in the bottom of the eighth, just to see the Red Raiders regain the lead in the top of the ninth.
